I '''Calvin Edwin "Cal" Ripken, Jr.''' (mibait Agosto 24, 1960), a mibansagang a "'''The [[Iron man (sports streak)|Iron man]]'''",<ref>{{Cite news|first=Christine|last=Destefano|title=Ripken is baseball's new Ironman|url=http://www.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20020808&content_id=99338&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=null|publisher=MLB.com|date=2002-08-08|accessdate=2007-07-30}}</ref> Americanu yang sadyang talapamyalung [[baseball]] [[shortstop]] ampong [[third baseman]] a memyalung adwang pulung (21) king [[Major League Baseball]] (MLB) para king [[Baltimore Orioles]] (1981–2001). Metung yang makata-labingsyam (19) a [[Major League Baseball All-Star Game|All-Star]] ampong makatadwa (''two-time'') [[American League]] (AL) [[Major League Baseball Most Valuable Player Award|Most Valuable Player (MVP)]], i Ripken, a mapalyaring pikabalwan dili uling bilbal ne ing gewa nang  [[Lou Gehrig]] a [[Major League Baseball consecutive games played fstreaks|record para kareng tuki-tuking pyalung a pikyabayan record for consecutive games played]] (''record for consecutive games played''), a melwat limampulu't anam (56) a banwa at tuturing da reng dakal a [[List of Major League Baseball records considered unbreakable|e malyaring balbalan]]. Ligpusan neng Ripken ing marka marka anyang Setiembre 6, 1995 kapamilatan ning pamamyalung king kayang ka-2,131 a pyalung,<ref>{{Cite news| url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/almanac/video/1995/index.html | work=CNN|title=Cal Ripken Jr. plays in his 2,131st consecutive game}}</ref> a kaybat inalal da reng  fans a later voted the "Most Memorable Moment" ("Most Memorable Moment") king kasalesayan ning MLB.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mlb.com/mlb/events/memorable_moments/mlb_memorable_moments.jsp|title=Major League Baseball Memorable Moments|publisher=MLB.com|accessdate=2007-07-30}}</ref> Kusa neng inaring Ripken ing kayang labingpitung banwang a pamitaglus-taglus (''17-year streak'') king ka-2,632ng pyalung anyang 1998.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/sports/baseball/ripken/bal-cal1998sep23,0,3104554.htmlstory|last=Strauss|first=Joe|work=[[Baltimore Sun]]|date=21 September 1998|title=After 2,632 consecutive games, Iron Man takes a seat|accessdate=10 January 2011}}</ref> Metung kareng pekaprodukibu panga-opensibung talapamyalung king kayang pusisyun i Ripken, a migtalang 3,184 [[Hit (baseball)|hits]], 431 [[home runs]], ampong 1,695 [[runs batted in]] king kayang karera, at sinambut yang adwang [[Gold Glove Award]] para king kayang depensa. 

